==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Austereness
<hw>Aus*tere"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Harshness or
astringent sourness to the taste; acerbity.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Severity; strictness; austerity.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Austerity</ent>⟦br⟧
